OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRMT rejects offer aimed at 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Faverting festive strikes   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The RMT union has rejected an offer    
OL,6, from the group representing train      
OL,7, companies which sought to stop strikes 
OL,8, in the run-up to Christmas.            
OL,10,FThe latest round of strikes by RMT     
OL,11,Fmembers at Network Rail and 14 train   
OL,12,Fcompanies is due to begin in nine days.
OL,14,FThe Rail Delivery Group (RDG) said its 
OL,15,Foffer included a pay increase for staff
OL,16,Fof up to 8% over two years.            
OL,18,FBut the RMT said it would lead to huge 
OL,19,Fjob losses and called for an urgent    
OL,20,Fmeeting with bosses on Monday.         
